  • Constructor Details

    • Trip

      public Trip​(Lodging lodging, Flight flight, java.lang.String duration, java.lang.String location)
      Parameters:
      lodging - the lodging associated with this trip. Can be null if this trip does not have a lodging.
      flight - the flight associated with this trip. Can be null if this trip does not have a flight.
      duration - the time between checkin and checkout.
      location - The location of the trip. Same as the location of the lodging if present.
